Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼無論UNION還是AEU都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.82,0:07:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請總裁利用手中的權限把我安置進軍中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你原本是所屬外籍軍團的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名號是蓋利·比亞吉少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對你的才能我有所耳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 為什麼如此想介入其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欠了人家三筆債
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然也有這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.54,0:07:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但以我的感覺 不再需要傭兵的時代即將到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.56,0:08:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以想去能夠戰鬥的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底知道多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說了這只是感覺而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多多關照 總裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 都怪那天什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.99,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,採訪落了個空 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才說總裁正在會客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是JNN的特派員 想打聽一點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JNN的記者小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然可以 但我有點趕時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不介意的話請上車說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻煩您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絹江·庫斯洛德小姐是麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不錯 有像您這麼漂亮的記者小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 您想打聽什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若說錯了請別見怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比亞吉先生剛才 是不是和列車公司的總裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格納·哈維氏會面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你們談了些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我經營物流業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了確認物資流通狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來向總裁報告的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特地向總裁報告？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 是私人使用的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不冒犯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能告訴我那些物資是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 是GN Drive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GN…Drive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是跟磁懸浮列車相關的器材嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是驅動MS的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Gundam的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.65,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「天人」所擁有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.28,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個庫爾吉斯少年士兵當機師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那架Gundam的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫爾吉斯的…少年士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誘拐後洗腦 使其接受戰鬥訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.76,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,培養成游擊隊士兵的 不瞞您說 就是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你 你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠打仗吃飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡打仗喜歡得要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.05,0:10:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵循人類原始衝動而活 差勁透頂的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐又出差了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩人的老鼠已經清理掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.28,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是能獲得輿論支持的正面宣傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 吃不飽的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路易絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.85,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸…爸爸  沙…沙慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.67,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,!Effect,{\fs20\an2}UNION 高軌道空間站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞里桑德羅大人何必親自前來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你費盡千辛萬苦才獲得的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓我親眼見識一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 這也是科納一族長久以來的夙願啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.99,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞里桑德羅大人 不 科納家早在三代以前就在謀求介入計劃的機會了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要有Veda在 我們就無能為力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.76,0:12:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時偶然間 一位天使降臨在我的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你 利馮茲·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知遇之恩 無以為報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.08,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒想到會找到本體的所在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 花了這麼長時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利馮茲 你就是我名副其實的天使啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.88,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非洲大陸 西北部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拚死拚活給他們干 卻突然不來聯繫 搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別問我 妮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不擅長考慮這麼複雜的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米迦哥確實是這種類型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.75,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好你個哈羅 想被挨千刀嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.82,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米迦勒 哈羅是Trinity不可或缺的戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥 剛才是開玩笑而已 開玩笑的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格納發來了任務計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內容和平時一樣 三天後開始行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我好等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 怎麼突破保安系統的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.16,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係 總之看到這裏就別想活著回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下米迦勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.45,0:14:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位女士我曾在Veda的資料裏看到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很榮幸能留在你的記憶中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我名叫王留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在為「天人」做特工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位是我的搭檔 紅龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是個好男人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.34,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能到這裏來 說明了你的能力之高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 找我們有何貴幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是來打聲招呼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Trinity小隊和我們同屬「天人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.24,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為特工 我們來協助你們是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是遭到了你們Gundam的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事有所耳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.67,0:14:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我也並非那邊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 保持中立立場？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.35,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我歸根到底是 支持伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格理念的人之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 王留美 需要時 我們會期待你的援助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡力而為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別向他們透露這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向你們保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好嗎 大哥 那麼快就放他們回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.64,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼大不了的 手頭的牌越多越有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個美人兒 是個美人兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別鬧彆扭 別鬧彆扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.43,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好嗎 大小姐 「天人」正和他們處於敵對狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.04,0:15:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無妨 Trinity誘發了世界的變革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.36,0:15:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您就這麼討厭當今的世界嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.54,0:16:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 再一成不變的話 我甚至希望它就此毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Exia著艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時沒有變化 Trinity也保持沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請下令懲罰我們的違令行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.11,0:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.10,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皇小姐 Trinity有動靜了
